label: 10002080-13x
info_overview: Roller Blind IO is ready to operate with Z-Wave controllers and configured to be managed by Simon100 IO APP using the HUB plug IO for getting a better user experience. Sending the Blind Up/Down or setting a specific position.
info_inclusion:
When the pushbutton is released after a press of (2<T<10sec) the device will send a NIF to include from Z-Wave network or perform an association with other Z-Wave device.

Central LED will Blink with 0,3 sec period to inform that NIF can be send after release of pushbutton.

This process does not perform a default reset of configurations.

Main LED will Blink with 0,3 sec period to inform that NIF can be send after release of pushbutton.
info_exclusion:
When the pushbutton is released after a press of (2<T<10sec) the device will send a NIF to exclude from Z-Wave network or perform an association with other Z-Wave device.

Main LED will Blink with 0,3 sec period to inform that NIF can be send after release of pushbutton.

This process does not perform a default reset of configurations.

Main LED will Blink with 0,3 sec period to inform that NIF can be send after release of pushbutton.

options.label: Sets the UP time in seconds
options.overview: 0x01-0x78 Sets the UP time of Sunblind in seconds

options.label: Sets the DOWN time in seconds
options.overview: 0x01-0x78 Sets the DOWN time of Sunblind in seconds

parameters.label: Calibration
parameters.overview: 255 - The device will perform a calibration process in order to Set the UP and DOWN times automatically

parameters.label: Behavior of LED in Repose
parameters.description: Configuration of Main LED as identification at 20%.

options.label: LED ON at 20% of maximum level

parameters.label: Lock Input
parameters.description: Unlock/lock the direct control of load.

options.label: Unlock the direct control of load.
Lock the direct control of load.
It is necessary to calibrate the device.
Long press works as overview.
options.overview:
Hold Press from 2sec to 20 sec does not performs a Node info.

Hold Press of 10 to 15 does not performs a automatic callibration.

Hold press of 15 to 30 does not changes the sunblind or awing changes.

Hold press of 30sec restores configuration except Lock Hold Press, and sends a Node info in order to add or remove from Z-Wave Network

associations.label: Lifeline
associations.overview:
Change on Sunblind position:

  • On -> CC Basic, Basic Report.
  • Value 0x01 - 0x63 Report sunblind position

Calibration requirement change. (If device needs to be calibrated and is Added into a ZWave network, it will report after receive an Association Set of life line).

  • Calibration required -> CC Configuration, Configuration Report, Param 23, Value 0xF
  • Calibration not required -> CC Configuration, Configuration Report, Param 23, Value 0x00

associations.label: ctrl
associations.overview:
Change on Sunblind position:

  • CC Basic, Basic Report.
  • Value 0x00 - 0x63 Report sunblind position
